[thinking] I’m thinking about how adding something explicit doesn’t prevent the ServiceLoader issue. If metadata is missing for the service loader, the native-image might fail—has this been supported yet? I wonder if the appengine-api includes service provider resources. Maybe the Forge agent generates those? But what about dynamic access? It seems we’re not editing the metadata. Could we entirely avoid the ServiceFactoryFactory? Actually, no, because AppEngineCredentials uses that factory.
[thinking] 
[assistant-event] thinking_end
